<br>
I've said it before and I'll say it again, if you form your opinion about someone by second hand information and logs and screenshots that could be doctored, you're a fool.  Make up your own mind, if you find the soapbox flame was correct after dealing with the person, cool.  If not, and the instigator turns out to be a liar, you would have passed up the opportunity to meet a decent or nice person.<br>
